# ------------------------------- start overview ------------------------------- # 
    ==> Quick view: sandbox attribute is a new attribute of the element iframe.

    ==> sandbox values:
        - sandbox="": forms,scripts,and plugins are disabled, features that trigger automatically are blocked, no links can target other browsing context.
        - sandbox="ALLOW-SCRIPT": allow script execution.
        - sandbox="ALLOW-FORMS": allows form submission.
        - sandbox="ALLOW-TOP-NAVIGATION": allows the iframe content to navigate its top-level browseing context.
# ------------------------------- start overview ------------------------------- # 